content: Incredible that a city can change so much in just a few years. My understanding of blockchain has evolved too. Fascinating how it all connects.
Looking back at my time in Japan, it's clear I'm not the same person who left NYC. The journey's reshaped me, just like the city.
AI is reshaping everything we thought we knew. Years of coding have taught me to embrace change, not fear it.
The markets are like NYC itself - unpredictable, yet full of opportunity. My algorithm's learning to dance to this tune.
Remember when we thought blockchain was just for crypto? Now, it's a lens through which I see the world. And NYC is my canvas.
